# Test Case Template

## Format
- ID
- Title
- Preconditions
- Test data
- Steps
- Expected result
- Actual result (if available)
- Priority or severity
- Tags (object, feature, test type)

## Example
- ID: TC-ACC-001
- Title: Create Account as Sales user
- Preconditions: User with Sales profile, Record Type "Business" is enabled
- Test data: Name=Acme, Industry=Manufacturing
- Steps:
  1. Open the Accounts tab.
  2. Click New.
  3. Fill in Name and Industry.
  4. Save the record.
- Expected result: Record is created, Record Type is Business, fields are accessible per FLS.
- Priority or severity: P1/High
- Tags: Account, UI, CRUD
